data.description: This charming home has 2000 sqft of living space. This gem, which has 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, has 2 gas fireplaces for cozy nights and a humidifying system. Many upgrades: new carpeting throughout the lower level, new paint in the downstairs living room, stylish new lighting, as well as beautiful original wood flooring. The fenced-in backyard has been beautifully landscaped with perennials, landscape lighting, well-fed UGS, and cement curbing, making it easy to enjoy the outdoors. The covered back patio is a nice place to enjoy your morning coffee, lunch, or dinner during the warmer months. Parks, hiking, walking trails and local shopping in close range of the home, which offers modern living. Don't miss out on the opportunity to call this beautifully maintained property your own.
